\begin_inset Formula \[
h(i)=\left[0.0201,1.280\times10^{-7},5.982\times10^{-5},0.01242,0.9674\right]\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Applying the convolution operator to 
\begin_inset Formula $n(i)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $h(i)$
\end_inset

